                <h3 id="helper-classes-backgrounds">情境背景色</h3>
                <p>和情境文本颜色类一样，使用任意情境背景色类就可以设置元素的背景。链接组件在鼠标经过时颜色会加深，就像上面所讲的情境文本颜色类一样。</p>
                <div class="bs-example bs-example-bg-classes" data-example-id="contextual-backgrounds-helpers">
                    <p><a class="bg-primary text-white" href="javascript:;">------为了突出显示，增加了text-white------</a></p>
                    <p><a class="bg-success" href="javascript:;">Duis mollis, est non commodo luctus, nisi erat porttitor ligula.</a></p>
                    <p><a class="bg-info" href="javascript:;">Maecenas sed diam eget risus varius blandit sit amet non magna.</a></p>
                    <p><a class="bg-warning" href="javascript:;">Etiam porta sem malesuada magna mollis euismod.</a></p>
                    <p><a class="bg-danger" href="javascript:;">Donec ullamcorper nulla non metus auctor fringilla.</a></p>
                    <p><a class="bg-whitesmoke" href="javascript:;">--------适合作为APP的默认背景色-------------</a></p>
                    <p><a class="bg-white" href="javascript:;">Using color to add meaning only provides a visual indication.</a></p>
                    <p><a class="bg-black text-white" href="javascript:;">------为了突出显示，增加了text-white------</a></p>
